  "voice_design": {
    "elevenlabs_preferred": true,
    "voice_design_prompt": "A mid-low male voice in his late 30s, dry and technical, with a baritone-adjacent register. Conversational pace but not rushed. Dry humor under every other sentence \u2014 the kind of dry where the smile is in the word choice, not the delivery. Precise diction, minimal vocal fry, no upspeak. Sounds like someone who's patiently explained the same concept six ways and is about to try a seventh. Good for technical correction, calm logging, wry observations.",
